body:
###

![AMS' Easy Coordinates](https://i.postimg.cc/90WgyYKY/MUTE-Title-1.png)

**AMS' Easy Coordinates** gives you quick access to your in-game XYZ coordinates right on the screen. It also allows you to quickly share your coordinates with other players via chat. 

![Base feature](https://i.postimg.cc/hj4wQ7vm/Screenshot-1.png)
![Share coordinates](https://i.postimg.cc/SNYP94Sg/Screenshot-2.png)

### Features:
- On-Screen Coordinates;
- Send Coordinates in chat (configurable in settings - default key is **dot**);
- Sending coordinates in chat has a 5 second cooldown to prevent spam - You can remove this by editing the *.toml* file under your minecraft *config* folder;

If you enjoy this mod, consider [supporting my work.](https://buymeacoffee.com/alexmsa
